Command Structures:
Opening brace on the SAME LINE as the declaration. Closing brace on a new line.

e.g. if(this == notTheBestWay){
          //You are wrong.
     }
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------     
Variables:
Begin first word w/ lower case, subsequent words w/ upper case. No underscore, 

e.g fooBar
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Data Members:
Same as variables but begin with 'f'

e.g. fBaz
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Classes:
Begin all words w/ capital

e.g. MyBigBoyClass
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Functions & Methods:
Same as variables,

e.g. fooBar()
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pre-processor Constants
All capital, begin with C_

e.g. C_BAZ
